the prime directive ... .. okay , this was n't too bad . the plot is about the prime directive and what it means . well , an alien force and certain star fleet members express interest in a planet with regenerative properties . their interests violates star fleet 's golden rule , `` the prime directive '' . the federation may not interfere in the development of other civilizations . picard makes a very hard choice and go against star fleet 's golden rule . picard and his crew must protect and defend the planet . even if it means the end of their careers at star fleet .